			"prompt": "Sometimes I do get a little lonely, like anyone. But when you're talking to me like this, any loneliness just <pitch mult=\"1.3\">flies</pitch> out the window. <break size=\"0.7\"/> I <pitch mult=\"1.3\">wonder</pitch> where it goes.",
